  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.1">
<l>vaikuntā maṇivaṇṇaṉē yeṉpollāt tirukuṟaḷā veṉṉuṇ maṉṉi</l>
<l>vaikum vaika ṟōṟu mamutāya vāṉēṟē</l>
<l>ceykun tāvarun tīmaiyuṉ ṉaṭiyārkkut tīrttacurarkkut tīmaikaḷ</l>
<l>ceykuntā vuṉṉaināṉ piṭittēṉkoḷ cikkeṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from Vaikunta, sapphire-coloured one, dwelling in my heart as my wicked sacred dwarf,</l>
<l>o divine bull who is ambrosia every passing day,</l>
<l>o Kunda flower from the fields who ends the difficult evil for his servants [and] does evils to the Asuras,</l>
<l>o Kunda, you I grip firmly – take [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
